  "title": "🚀 No experience? Still hired. 🚀",
  "description": "<p>🎬 <strong>Where Ambition Meets Energy — Welcome to Valor Organisation</strong></p><p>We’re <strong>Valor Organisation</strong>, a fast-growing marketing team based in Singapore. We move quickly, think boldly, and build campaigns that connect brands with real people. If you’re motivated, sharp, and ready to grow, you’ll feel right at home here.<br /></p><p>🎯 <strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p><ul><li><p>Execute high-impact marketing campaigns</p></li><li><p>Communicate with clients and present strong ideas</p></li><li><p>Work closely with a driven team that values performance and progress<br /></p></li></ul><p>💎 <strong>What You’ll Gain</strong></p><ul><li><p>A positive, high-energy environment that celebrates results</p></li><li><p>Practical, hands-on experience in marketing and sales</p></li><li><p>Opportunities to travel, learn, and broaden your exposure</p></li><li><p>A role that challenges you and keeps you engaged<br /></p></li></ul><p>💪 <strong>Who We’re Looking For</strong></p><ul><li><p>Fresh graduates, ORD-completed candidates, or career switchers</p></li><li><p>Individuals with a positive attitude and strong work ethic</p></li><li><p>Fast learners who thrive in collaborative, goal-driven teams<br /></p></li></ul><p>🚀 <strong>If you’re hungry to learn, ready to perform, and want a career with momentum — this is your next move.</strong></p>",
